INSERT INTO contract
            (
                contract_id,
                date_expired,
                date_issued,
                issuer_corporation_id,
                issuer_id,
                typ,

                title,

                -- item exchange
                price,

                -- auction
                buyout,

                -- hauling
                collateral,
                days_to_complete,
                for_corporation,
                reward,
                end_location_id,
                start_location_id,
                volume
            )
            SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                $1::BIGINT[],
                $2::TIMESTAMP[],
                $3::TIMESTAMP[],
                $4::INTEGER[],
                $5::INTEGER[],
                $6::VARCHAR[],
                $7::VARCHAR[],
                $8::FLOAT[],
                $9::FLOAT[],
                $10::FLOAT[],
                $11::INTEGER[],
                $12::BOOLEAN[],
                $13::FLOAT[],
                $14::BIGINT[],
                $15::BIGINT[],
                $16::FLOAT[]
            )
            ON CONFLICT (contract_id)
            DO NOTHING
